_beneficiaries_1_name','field_5a6a6dce17341'),(1204,198,'beneficiaries_1_description','For over 30 years, Heal the Bay has led the Los Angeles fight for our great ocean. EFFERVESCENCE is proud to support their environmental stewardship and water advocacy efforts here in the Southland, as we partner to protect the Pacific and related waterways.'),(1205,198,'_beneficiaries_1_description','field_5a6a6dd517342'),(1206,198,'beneficiaries_1_logo','436'),(1207,198,'_beneficiaries_1_logo','field_5a6a6de317343'),(1208,198,'beneficiaries_1_photo',''),(1209,198,'_beneficiaries_1_photo','field_5a6a6e7f17346'),(1210,198,'beneficiaries','2'),(1211,198,'_beneficiaries','field_5a6a6dc017340'),(1212,198,'beneficiaries_0_website','https://www.tjmartell.org'),(1213,198,'_beneficiaries_0_website','field_5a6a76f16e540'),(1214,198,'beneficiaries_1_website','https://www.healthebay.org'),(1215,198,'_beneficiaries_1_website','field_5a6a76f16e540'),(1218,124,'event_options_event_hide_guide_btn','1'),(1219,124,'_event_options_event_hide_guide_btn','field_5a625ed82515e'),(1220,124,'event_options_event_show_faq_btn','1'),(1221,124,'_event_options_event_show_faq_btn','field_5a625efa2515f'),(1222,124,'event_options',''),(1223,124,'_event_options','field_5a625eb82515d'),(1345,215,'_edit_lock','1525650137:4'),(1346,215,'_edit_last','4'),(1347,215,'event_type','2'),(1348,215,'_event_type','field_5a621223b7bc7'),(1349,215,'event_excerpt','The can’t miss event of Effervescence! Join us for a grand tasting tour of Champagne and all the region has to offer. Come anytime, but we recommend joining us by 3:30pm. All wines are included in the ticket price!'),(1350,215,'_event_excerpt','field_5a621b80bbd03'),(1351,215,'event_content','The pinnacle of the weekend, our walk-around style Grand Champagne tasting is an all-out homage to Champagne in all its varied expressions.\r\n\r\nWe’ve carefully curated a line-up of the region’s finest – from rare artisanal grower Champagnes made in miniscule quantities to extraordinary vintage bottlings to tête de cuvée trophy wines from the legendary Grande Marques, this is the place to taste them all in one location.\r\n<blockquote>\r\n<h3>This is the must-attend event in Los Angeles for anyone serious about Champagne</h3>\r\n&nbsp;</blockquote>\r\nNo other event in America has yet offered this kind of comprehensive tasting opportunity for both aspiring enthusiasts and seasoned collectors. It is the must-attend event in Los Angeles for anyone serious about Champagne, and we can’t wait to raise a glass (or three) with you there.'),(1352,215,'_event_content','field_5a621095d626c'),(1353,215,'event_package','a:1:{i:0;s:3:\"139\";}'),(1354,215,'_event_package','field_5a6222a9f43c7'),(1355,215,'event_passes','1'),(1356,215,'_event_passes','field_5a625f5e1c1fe'),(1357,215,'event_venue','40'),(1358,215,'_event_venue','field_5a6224a7dde1d'),(1359,215,'event_start_date','20180505'),(1360,215,'_event_start_date','field_5a622aacf8cf9'),(1361,215,'event_start_time','13:00:00'),(1362,215,'_event_start_time','field_5a622acff8cfa'),(1363,215,'event_end_time','17:00:00'),(1364,215,'_event_end_time','field_5a622b05f8cfb'),(1365,215,'event_participant_groups','1'),(1366,215,'_event_participant_groups','field_5a6224cad31dc'),(1367,215,'event_banner','372'),(1368,215,'_event_banner','field_5a6260de00b05'),(1369,215,'event_sidebar_image',''),(1370,215,'_event_sidebar_image','field_5a6260fa00b06'),(1371,215,'event_thumbnail','321'),(1372,215,'_event_thumbnail','field_5a69fb1602917'),(1373,215,'event_options_event_hide_guide_btn','1'),(1374,215,'_event_options_event_hide_guide_btn','field_5a625ed82515e'),(1375,215,'event_options_event_show_faq_btn','1'),(1376,215,'_event_options_event_show_faq_btn','field_5a625efa2515f'),(1377,215,'event_options',''),(1378,215,'_event_options','field_5a625eb82515d'),(1379,215,'_yoast_wpseo_content_score','30'),(1444,219,'post_content','Nam interdum volutpat orci ut volutpat. Nunc non mattis nulla, ut consequat mi. Aliquam 