ty and contemporary value of these legendary bubbles.\r\n\r\n<strong>Wines to poured:</strong>\r\n\r\nRiunart Blanc de Blancs\r\nDom Ruinart Blanc de Blancs 2006\r\n\r\nLouis Roederer Brut Premier\r\nLouis Roederer Cristal 2009\r\n\r\nBollinger Brut Special Cuvée\r\nBollinger Grande Année 2007\r\n\r\n&nbsp;'),(2252,243,'_event_content','field_5a621095d626c'),(2253,243,'event_package',''),(2254,243,'_event_package','field_5a6222a9f43c7'),(2255,243,'event_passes','1'),(2256,243,'_event_passes','field_5a625f5e1c1fe'),(2257,243,'event_venue','114'),(2258,243,'_event_venue','field_5a6224a7dde1d'),(2259,243,'event_start_date','20180503'),(2260,243,'_event_start_date','field_5a622aacf8cf9'),(2261,243,'event_start_time','13:30:00'),(2262,243,'_event_start_time','field_5a622acff8cfa'),(2263,243,'event_end_time','15:00:00'),(2264,243,'_event_end_time','field_5a622b05f8cfb'),(2265,243,'event_participant_groups','1'),(2266,243,'_event_participant_groups','field_5a6224cad31dc'),(2267,243,'event_banner',''),(2268,243,'_event_banner','field_5a6260de00b05'),(2269,243,'event_sidebar_image',''),(2270,243,'_event_sidebar_image','field_5a6260fa00b06'),(2271,243,'event_thumbnail','457'),(2272,243,'_event_thumbnail','field_5a69fb1602917'),(2273,243,'event_options_event_hide_guide_btn','1'),(2274,243,'_event_options_event_hide_guide_btn','field_5a625ed82515e'),(2275,243,'event_options_event_show_faq_btn','1'),(2276,243,'_event_options_event_show_faq_btn','field_5a625efa2515f'),(2277,243,'event_options',''),(2278,243,'_event_options','field_5a625eb82515d'),(2279,243,'_yoast_wpseo_content_score','30'),(2280,244,'_edit_lock','1527197202:4'),(2281,244,'_edit_last','4'),(2282,244,'event_type','4'),(2283,244,'_event_type','field_5a621223b7bc7'),(2284,244,'event_excerpt','Noted journalist Patrick Comiskey on the international breadth of sparkling wines.\r\n\r\nIf you prefer to purchase tickets by phone, please call one of the numbers below, leave your name and number and we will gladly reach out to take your order: <a href=\"tel://323.499.8678\">323.499.8678</a> and <a href=\"tel://323.937.9463\">323.937.9463</a>.'),(2285,244,'_event_excerpt','field_5a621b80bbd03'),(2286,244,'event_content','While Champagne holds its place as the world leader in sparkling wine production, the rest of the planet has been busily catching up.  Increasingly, American market share is divided amidst high-quality sparkling wines from Italy, Spain, Germany, Austria and the US. (Just don’t call them Champagne!)\r\n<blockquote>\r\n<h3>An examination of international sparkling wines sourced from around the globe.</h3>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nPatrick Comiskey, lead wine writer for the <em>Los Angeles Times</em> among many other publications, joins Effervescence to lead an examination of international sparkling wines sourced from around the globe.  From Italian winners like prosecco, moscato and Franciacorta bubblies to sensational Spanish cava and top-notch American sparklers, there’s a growing world of sparkling wines to be discovered and at all price-points too.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong>Wines to be poured:</strong>\r\n\r\nRidgeview 2014 Cavendish Brut\r\nHush Heath Balfour BdB\r\n\r\nDom de Montbourgeau Cremant de Jura\r\nFrancois Chidaine Montlouis Brut Nature\r\n\r\nAnalemma 2013 Atavus BdN\r\nIron Horse 2013 Brut X\r\n\r\nArras 2008 Grand Vintage Brut\r\nNo. 1 Family NV BdB'),(2287,244,'_event_content','field_5a621095d626c'),(2288,244,'event_package',''),(2289,244,'_event_package','field_5a6222a9f43c7'),(2290,244,'event_passes_0_title','Master Class Pass'),(2291,244,'_event_passes_0_title','field_5a625f711c1ff'),(2292,244,'event_passes_0_price','$70'),(2293,244,'_event_passes_0_price','field_5a625fa91c200'),(2294,244,'event_passes_0_description',''),(2295,244,'_event_passes_0_description','field_5a625fc61c201'),(2296,244,'event_passes','1'),(2297,244,'_event_passes','field_5a625f5e1c1fe'),(2298,244,'event_venue','114'),(2299,244,'_event_venue','field_5a6224a7dde1d')