s bubbles inside and out.  The Best Sparkling Somm competition is open to any accredited American sommelier with demonstrated restaurant experience and a core competency in both viticulture and vinification practices. <strong>N</strong><b>ominations closed on March 31st, 2018.</b>\r\n\r\nEFFERVESCENCE selected twelve finalists!\r\n\r\nNot just a popularity contest, our competition finalists had to also complete a timed online assessment of sparkling wine knowledge.  The top three composite scoring sommeliers will be flown to EFFERVESCENCE to compete on-stage on Friday night, May 4th at the Avalon Hollywood at our <a href=\"https://effervescencela.com/events/bubbles-sparkling-wine-extravanga/\">More Bubbles sparkling wine extravaganza</a>.  On-stage sommelier skills to be assessed by our panel of judges will include precision pouring and timed blind-tasting.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h4>Results of voting and examination</h4>\r\nThe results are in! Our three finalists for #BestSparklingSomm at Effervescence 2018 are <strong>Dana Farner</strong>, <strong>Wendy Shoemaker</strong> and <strong>Rachel Macalisang</strong>. Congrats ladies! Join us as we get to see their on-stage skills live on Friday night at the <a href=\"https://effervescencela.com/events/bubbles-sparkling-wine-extravanga/\">More Bubbles sparkling wine extravaganza</a><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: #333333; cursor: text; font-family: Georgia,\'Times New Roman\',\'Bitstream Charter\',Times,serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px;\">.</span>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h4>Eligibility and nominations</h4>\r\nOpen only to accredited sommeliers, the nominations for qualified candidates for 2018 has now closed.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong>Winner</strong>\r\n\r\nA huge congratulations to our first #BestSparklingSomm, <b>Wendy Shoemaker</b>, who took home the title on May 4 at the More Bubbles Sparkling Wine event.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h4>Prize</h4>\r\nThe Grand Prize for the <strong>#bestsparklingsomm</strong> winner will be a trip to Champagne including airfare, accommodations and access to exclusive tastings.\r\n\r\n<span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: #333333; cursor: text; font-family: Georgia,\'Times New Roman\',\'Bitstream Charter\',Times,serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px;\">If you have any questions regarding the sommelier competition, please send us an </span><a href=\"mailto:bonnie@effervescencela.com\">email here</a><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: #333333; cursor: text; font-family: Georgia,\'Times New Roman\',\'Bitstream Charter\',Times,serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px;\">.</span>\r\n<p style=\"font-size: 90%;\">Contestants must be 21 years of age with verifiable industry experience. Sommeliers may nominate themselves or colleagues. Eligibility to be determined by Effervescence event team. No purchase necessary to participate.</p>'),(2457,93,'_post_content_bottom','field_5a7b55bcc6d9b'),(2458,97,'post_content','As part of our inaugural EFFERVESCENCE program, we’ve invited the crème de la crème of the wine industry to join us - and you - in an exploration of all things sparkling in our series of master classes.  From Master Sommeliers to esteemed authors, and winemakers, our speakers look forward to engaging you in dynamic discussion about their specialties, while we taste through an inimitable line-up of Champagne and sparkling wine. Don\'t miss this unique opportunity to hear some of the top experts share their intimate knowledge as you taste wines carefully selected for each class.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;'),(2459,97,'_post_content','field_5a7b55a6c6d9a'),(2460,97,'post_content_bottom',''),(2461,97,'_post_content_bottom','field_5a7b55bcc6d9b'),(2462,95,'post_content','What is wine without food?  At EFFERVESCENCE, we firmly believe that Champagne and sparkling wines are the perfect complement to ANY food, from street vendors to haute cuisine.  No longer relegated to aperitifs or toasts, Champagnes and sparkling wines in their full range of expression can be expertly paired with an extraordinary range of foods.\r\n\r\nAs we begin our celebration in Los Angeles, we are deeply honored to welcome three of our city’s very best – Chefs Walter Manzke,  Casey Lane and Kevin Meehan – as our 2018 EFFERVESCENCE festival chefs.'),(2463,95,'_post_content','field_5a7b55a6c6d9a'),(2464,95,'post_content_bottom',''),(2465,95,'_post_content_bottom','field_5a7b55bcc6d9b'),(2470,232,'_yoast_wpseo_focuskw_text_input','sparkling wine'),(2471,232,'_yoast_wpseo_focuskw','sparkling wine'),(2472,232,'_yoast_wpseo_linkdex','32'),(2480,284,'_edit_last','4'),(2481,284,'_wp_page_template','template-about.php'),(2482,284,'_yoast_wpseo_content_score','30'),(2483,284,'_edit_lock','1548367078:5'),(2484,285,'_menu_item_type','post_type'),(2485,285,'_menu_item_menu_item_parent','0'),(2486,285,'_menu_item_object_id','284'),(2487,285,'_menu_item_object','page'),(2488,285,'_menu_item_target',''),(2489,285,'_menu_item_classes','a:1:{i:0;s:0:\"\";}'),(2490,285,'_menu_item_xfn',''),(2491,285,'_menu_item_url',''),(2513,289,'_wp_attached_file','2018/02/beneficiary-logo-fish-white.png'),(2514,289,'_wp_attachment_metadata','a: