nd the world, EFFERVESCENCE brings them all to you in one epic Los Angeles weekend of celebrating bubbles. This action-packed festival includes master classes led by world-renowned experts, gourmet meals prepared by acclaimed chefs and walk-around wine tastings where you\'ll have the chance to taste just about everything that sparkles. Come hungry, come thirsty, come curious... EFFERVESCENCE is ready to welcome you.'),(2815,284,'_post_content','field_5a7f067bcddaa'),(2816,284,'post_banner','377'),(2817,284,'_post_banner','field_5a7f0721daba2'),(2822,306,'_yoast_wpseo_focuskw_text_input','Champagne'),(2823,306,'_yoast_wpseo_focuskw','Champagne'),(2824,306,'_yoast_wpseo_title','Effervescence - A Champagne & Sparkling Wine Celebration'),(2825,306,'_yoast_wpseo_metadesc','Champagne Tasting event in Los Angeles. America’s first epicurean festival centered only on Champagne and sparkling wines, all in one epic weekend of tastings, masterclasses, gourmet pairings and a Champagne Gala Dinner. The event features wine producers, sommeliers, chefs, and speakers from around the globe.'),(2826,306,'_yoast_wpseo_linkdex','30'),(2827,86,'post_content','EFFERVESCENCE is proud to be the premier American showcase for the very finest in Champagne and sparkling wines. Please see the list of represented producers for our inaugural Grand Champagne Tasting and More Bubbles Sparkling Wine Extravaganza, and read more about the story behind each brand.'),(2828,86,'_post_content','field_5a7f067bcddaa'),(2829,86,'post_banner','382'),(2830,86,'_post_banner','field_5a7f0721daba2'),(2835,284,'clone_general_page_content',''),(2836,284,'_clone_general_page_content','field_5a83d28753f90'),(2837,284,'about_address','Effervescence – 8383 Wilshire Blvd – Suite 800 – Beverly Hills, CA 90211'),(2838,284,'_about_address','field_5a83e6c44b008'),(2839,284,'about_founders_0_name','Dan Perrelli'),(2840,284,'_about_founders_0_name','field_5a83d2d308f31'),(2841,284,'about_founders_0_url',''),(2842,284,'_about_founders_0_url','field_5a83d2de08f32'),(2843,284,'about_founders_0_description','<a href=\"mailto:dan@effervescencela.com\">Managing Partner</a>\r\n<br />\r\n<br />Dan Perrelli is a Los Angeles-based wine connoisseur and owner of wine retailer First the Wine / Then the Story, who has dedicated his life to making the improbable probable.\r\n \r\n\r\n'),(2844,284,'_about_founders_0_description','field_5a83d30208f34'),(2845,284,'about_founders_0_photo',''),(2846,284,'_about_founders_0_photo','field_5a83d2f808f33'),(2847,284,'about_founders_1_name','Jannika Pettersson'),(2848,284,'_about_founders_1_name','field_5a83d2d308f31'),(2849,284,'about_founders_1_url',''),(2850,284,'_about_founders_1_url','field_5a83d2de08f32'),(2851,284,'about_founders_1_description','<a href=\"mailto:jannika@effervescencela.com\">Partner & General Manager</a><br />\r\n<br />Jannika Pettersson is a Champagne lover with an international background, calling LA home since 2009. She left the marketing industry to pursue her passion by co-founding Effervescence.'),(2852,284,'_about_founders_1_description','field_5a83d30208f34'),(2853,284,'about_founders_1_photo',''),(2854,284,'_about_founders_1_photo','field_5a83d2f808f33'),(2863,284,'about_founders','2'),(2864,284,'_about_founders','field_5a83d2c708f30'),(2865,284,'clone_general_page_visuals',''),(2866,284,'_clone_general_page_visuals','field_5a83e6f0cb27f'),(2867,423,'_wp_attached_file','2018/02/open-graph-size-image.jpg'),(2868,423,'_wp_attachment_metadata','a:5:{s:5:\"width\";i:1200;s:6:\"height\";i:630;s:4:\"file\";s:33:\"2018/02/open-graph-size-image.jpg\";s:5:\"sizes\";a:5:{s:9:\"thumbnail\";a:4:{s:4:\"file\";s:33:\"open-graph-size-image-300x300.jpg\";s:5:\"width\";i:300;s:6:\"height\";i:300;s:9:\"mime-type\";s:10:\"image/jpeg\";}s:6:\"medium\";a:4:{s:4:\"file\";s:33:\"open-graph-size-image-800x420.jpg\";s:5:\"width\";i:800;s:6:\"height\";i:420;s:9:\"mime-type\";s:10:\"image/jpeg\";}s:12:\"medium_large\";a:4:{s:4:\"file\";s:33:\"open-graph-siz