oast_wpseo_focuskw_text_input','sparkling wine'),(2919,244,'_yoast_wpseo_focuskw','sparkling wine'),(2920,244,'_yoast_wpseo_metadesc','Effervescence, Los Angeles May 3-5, 2018. A deep dive into the world of sparkling wine. From prosecco, moscato, and Franciacorta to cava and top-notch American sparklers; join Patrick Comiskey, lead wine writer for the Los Angeles Times, on an examination of international sparkling wines sourced from around the globe.'),(2921,244,'_yoast_wpseo_linkdex','35'),(2922,243,'_yoast_wpseo_metadesc','Effervescence, May 3-5, 2018 in Los Angeles. A three day Champagne and sparkling wine festival with events happening day and night. Join Master Sommelier and noted wine educator Geoff Kruth for this comprehensive exploration and tasting of Champagnes from the Grande Marques.'),(2925,229,'_yoast_wpseo_metadesc','Effervescence, May 3-5, 2018 in Los Angeles. Join us on May 3rd for our Krug Lovers Champagne dinner, paired with the cuisine of Chef Casey Lane at Viale dei Romani.'),(2931,228,'_yoast_wpseo_focuskw_text_input','mature champagnes'),(2932,228,'_yoast_wpseo_focuskw','mature champagnes'),(2933,228,'_yoast_wpseo_metadesc','Effervescence, May 3-5, 2018 in Los Angeles. A three day festival celebrating Champagne and sparkling wine. Join us for this unique Master Class with international expert Richard Juhlin on the maturation process in Champagne, exemplified by a stunning line-up of mature champagnes.'),(2934,228,'_yoast_wpseo_linkdex','40'),(2935,236,'_yoast_wpseo_metadesc','Effervescence, May 3-5, 2018 in Los Angeles. A unique masterclass with Champagne expert Richard Juhlin on how the local environment influences our perception of sparkling wine, and how that led to the concept of Champagne Hiking.'),(2938,232,'_yoast_wpseo_metadesc','Effervescence May 3-5, 2018 in Los Angeles. An all you can (safely) drink, walk-around tasting featuring sparkling wine from around the globe.'),(2958,231,'_yoast_wpseo_focuskw_text_input','billecart-salmon'),(2959,231,'_yoast_wpseo_focuskw','billecart-salmon'),(2960,231,'_yoast_wpseo_metadesc','Effervescence, May 3-5, 2018 in Los Angeles. A three day festival celebrating Champagne and sparkling wine. Exclusive luncheon at République restaurant with Chef Walter Manzke honoring Billecart-Salmon\'s 200th anniversary.'),(2961,231,'_yoast_wpseo_linkdex','36'),(2965,198,'_yoast_wpseo_focuskw_text_input','beneficiaries'),(2966,198,'_yoast_wpseo_focuskw','beneficiaries'),(2967,198,'_yoast_wpseo_metadesc','Effervescence, May 3-5, 2018 in Los Angeles. Three days of celebrating Champagne and sparkling wine. A portion of the revenue from this event series will be shared with two non-profit beneficiaries with powerful impact in Los Angeles and beyond.'),(2968,198,'_yoast_wpseo_linkdex','56'),(2977,95,'_yoast_wpseo_focuskw_text_input','sparkling wine festival'),(2978,95,'_yoast_wpseo_focuskw','sparkling wine festival'),(2979,95,'_yoast_wpseo_metadesc','Effervescence, May 3-5, 2018 in Los Angeles. A three day Champagne and sparkling wine festival. For our inaugural event, we are excited to welcome three of LA\'s very best chefs: Walter Manzke, Casey Lane and Kevin Meehan. Join us for a series of exclusive gourmet experiences!'),(2980,95,'_yoast_wpseo_linkdex','43'),(2981,97,'_yoast_wpseo_focuskw_text_input','champagne and sparkling wine'),(2982,97,'_yoast_wpseo_focuskw','champagne and sparkling wine'),(2983,97,'_yoast_wpseo_metadesc','Effervescence, May 3-5, 2018 in Los Angeles. A three day Champagne and sparkling wine festival. As part of our inaugural EFFERVESCENCE event, we’ve invited several speakers to join us and you in an exploration of all things sparkling.'),(2984,97,'_yoast_wpseo_linkdex','42'),(2985,93,'_yoast_wpseo_focuskw_text_input','sommeliers'),(2986,93,'_yoast_wpseo_focuskw','sommeliers'),(2987,93,'_yoast_wpseo_metadesc','Effervescence, May 3-5, 2018. Champagne and sparkling wine festival in Los Angeles. Join us and our team of sommeliers carefully selected from America\'s best restaurants for a three day celebration of Champagne and sparkling wines.'),(2988,93,'_yoast_wpseo_linkdex','49'),(2992,86,'_yoast_wpseo_metadesc','Effervescence, May 3-5, 2018 in Los Angeles. Three day festival with wine tastings, master classes and gourmet meals. From extraordinary Champagnes to international sparkling wines, we are honored to be pouring quality wines from our participating producers.'),(2993,133,'_yoast_wpseo_focuskw_text_input','wine festival'),(2994,133,'_yoast_wpseo_focuskw','wine festival'),(2995,133,'_yoast_wpseo_metadesc','Effervescence, May 3-5, 2018 in Los Angeles. Proud to be partnering with our sponsors Angeleno Magazine, Krug, First the Wine and Vin du Cap for the inaugural three day Champagne and sparkling wine festival. Events include a Champagne tasting, a sparkling wine tasting and Champagne Gala Dinner.'),(2996,133,'_yoast_wpseo_linkdex','39'),(2997,284,'_yoast_wpseo_focuskw_text_input','effervescence'),(2998,284,'_yoast_wpseo_focuskw','effervescence'),(2999,284,'_yoast_wpseo_metadesc','Effervescence, Champange and sparkling wine festival, May 3-5, 2018 in Los Angeles. Three days with Champagne Grand Tasting and More Bubbles sparkling wine tasting, master classes, Collector Champagne luncheon, Collector Champagne dinner and a Champagne Gala dinner.'),(3000,284,'_yoast_wpseo_linkdex','57'),(3001,431,'_wp_attached_file','2018/02/Walter-Manzke_Headshot_Republique.jpeg.jpg'),(3002,431,'_wp_attachment_metadata','a:5:{s:5:\"width\";i:1367;s:6:\"height\";i:2048;s:4:\"file\";s:50:\"2018/02/Walter-Manzke_Headshot_Republique.jpeg.jpg\";s:5:\"sizes\";a:6:{s:9:\"thumbnail\";a:4:{s:4:\"file\";s:50:\"Walter-Manzke_Headshot_Republique.jpeg-300x300.jpg\";s:5:\"width\";i:300;s:6:\"height\";i:300;s:9:\"mime-type\";s:10:\"image/jpeg\";}s:6:\"medium\";a:4:{s:4:\"file\";s:50:\"Walter-Manzke_Headshot_Republique.jpeg-534x800.jpg\";s:5:\"width\";i:534;s:6:\"height\";i:800;s:9:\"mime-type\";s:10:\"image/jpeg\";}s:12:\"medium_large\";a:4:{s:4:\"