 prosecco, moscato, Lambrusco, cava, sekt, crémants and delicious American bubbles sourced from the finest international producers.\r\n<blockquote>\r\n<h3>Join us to sample prosecco, moscato, Lambrusco, cava and others.</h3>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n</p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>The evening will end with the first <a href=\"http://effervescencela.com/sommeliers/#competition\">Best Sparkling Somm</a> finals, where you will get to see today\'s best sommeliers compete against each other.</p>\r\n\r\nCome thirsty – your ticket price includes all you can (safely) drink. Cheers!'),(14880,1042,'_event_content','field_5a621095d626c'),(14881,1042,'event_package',''),(14882,1042,'_event_package','field_5a6222a9f43c7'),(14883,1042,'event_passes_0_title','More Bubbles Pass'),(14884,1042,'_event_passes_0_title','field_5a625f711c1ff'),(14885,1042,'event_passes_0_price','$125'),(14886,1042,'_event_passes_0_price','field_5a625fa91c200'),(14887,1042,'event_passes_0_description','Pass to our Friday afternoon tasting where you will get to taste exceptional sparkling wines from around the world.\r\n'),(14888,1042,'_event_passes_0_description','field_5a625fc61c201'),(14889,1042,'event_passes','1'),(14890,1042,'_event_passes','field_5a625f5e1c1fe'),(14891,1042,'event_venue','40'),(14892,1042,'_event_venue','field_5a6224a7dde1d'),(14893,1042,'event_start_date','20180504'),(14894,1042,'_event_start_date','field_5a622aacf8cf9'),(14895,1042,'event_start_time','16:30:00'),(14896,1042,'_event_start_time','field_5a622acff8cfa'),(14897,1042,'event_end_time','21:30:00'),(14898,1042,'_event_end_time','field_5a622b05f8cfb'),(14899,1042,'event_participant_groups_0_header','Participating Sparkling Wines (more to be confirmed)'),(14900,1042,'_event_participant_groups_0_header','field_5a6224e6d31dd'),(14901,1042,'event_participant_groups_0_producers','a:12:{i:0;s:2:\"85\";i:1;s:2:\"72\";i:2;s:3:\"115\";i:3;s:2:\"86\";i:4;s:2:\"70\";i:5;s:2:\"73\";i:6;s:2:\"68\";i:7;s:2:\"71\";i:8;s:3:\"116\";i:9;s:2:\"69\";i:10;s:3:\