s. Come hungry, come thirsty, come curious... EFFERVESCENCE is ready to welcome you.'),(23685,1385,'_post_content','field_5a7f067bcddaa'),(23686,1385,'post_banner','377'),(23687,1385,'_post_banner','field_5a7f0721daba2'),(23688,1385,'clone_general_page_content',''),(23689,1385,'_clone_general_page_content','field_5a83d28753f90'),(23690,1385,'about_address','Effervescence – 8383 Wilshire Blvd – Suite 800 – Beverly Hills, CA 90211'),(23691,1385,'_about_address','field_5a83e6c44b008'),(23692,1385,'about_founders_0_name','Dan Perrelli'),(23693,1385,'_about_founders_0_name','field_5a83d2d308f31'),(23694,1385,'about_founders_0_url',''),(23695,1385,'_about_founders_0_url','field_5a83d2de08f32'),(23696,1385,'about_founders_0_description','<a href=\"mailto:dan@effervescencela.com\">Managing Partner</a>\r\n<br />\r\n<br />Dan Perrelli is a Los Angeles-based wine connoisseur and owner of wine retailer First the Wine / Then the Story, who has dedicated his life to making the improbable probable.\r\n \r\n\r\n'),(23697,1385,'_about_founders_0_description','field_5a83d30208f34'),(23698,1385,'about_founders_0_photo',''),(23699,1385,'_about_founders_0_photo','field_5a83d2f808f33'),(23700,1385,'about_founders_1_name','Jannika Pettersson'),(23701,1385,'_about_founders_1_name','field_5a83d2d308f31'),(23702,1385,'about_founders_1_url',''),(23703,1385,'_about_founders_1_url','field_5a83d2de08f32'),(23704,1385,'about_founders_1_description','<a href=\"mailto:jannika@effervescencela.com\">Partner & General Manager</a><br />\r\n<br />Jannika Pettersson is a Champagne lover with an international background, calling LA home since 2009. She left the marketing industry to pursue her passion by co-founding Effervescence.'),(23705,1385,'_about_founders_1_description','field_5a83d30208f34'),(23706,1385,'about_founders_1_photo',''),(23707,1385,'_about_founders_1_photo','field_5a83d2f808f33'),(23708,1385,'about_founders','2'),(23709,1385,'_about_founders','field_5a83d2c708f30'),(23710,1385,'clone_general_page_visuals',''),(23711,1385,'_clone_general_page_visuals','field_5a83e6f0cb27f'),(23716,1388,'post_content','EFFERVESCENCE is proud to be the premier American showcase for the very finest in Champagne and sparkling wines. Please see the list of represented producers for our inaugural Grand Champagne Tasting and More Bubbles Sparkling Wine Extravaganza, and read more about the story behind each brand.\r\n\r\nMore wine producers to be announced soon.'),(23717,1388,'_post_content','field_5a7f067bcddaa'),(23718,1388,'post_banner','382'),(23719,1388,'_post_banner','field_5a7f0721daba2'),(23750,1392,'participant_archive_type','speaker'),(23751,1392,'_participant_archive_type','field_5a6980c871b49'),(23752,1392,'post_content','As part of our inaugural EFFERVESCENCE program, we’ve invited the crème de la crème of the wine industry to join us - and you - in an exploration of all things sparkling in our series of master classes.  From Master Sommeliers to esteemed authors, and winemakers, our speakers look forward to engaging you in dynamic discussion about their specialties, while we taste through an inimitable line-up of Champagnes and sparkling wines. Don\'t miss this unique opportunity to hear some of the top experts share their intimate knowledge as you taste wines carefully selected for each class.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;'),(23753,1392,'_post_content','field_5a7b55a6c6d9a'),(23754,1392,'post_content_bottom',''),(23755,1392,'_post_content_bottom','field_5a7b55bcc6d9b'),(23756,1392,'post_content_bottom_html_id',''),(23757,1392,'_post_content_bottom_html_id','field_5a7f04c135569'),(23758,1392,'post_banner','379'),(23759,1392,'_post_banner','field_5a7f0721daba2'),(23760,1392,'clone_page_banner_image_field',''),(23761,1392,'_clone_page_banner_image_field','field_5a7f07e0aeb45'),(23762,1392,'post_content_top_html_id',''),(23763,1392,'_post_content_top_html_id','field_5a85ca8f65e11'),(23764,1393,'participant_archive_type','speaker'),(23765,1393,'_participant_archive_type','field