23b7bc7'),(26418,1474,'event_excerpt','Join Effervescence as the famed Krug Champagne House takes over one of LA’s finest restaurants, Kali, for one night only.\r\n\r\nIf you prefer to purchase tickets by phone, please call one of the numbers below, leave your name and number and we will gladly reach out to take your order: <a href=\"tel://323.499.8678\">323.499.8678</a> and <a href=\"tel://323.937.9463\">323.937.9463</a>.'),(26419,1474,'_event_excerpt','field_5a621b80bbd03'),(26420,1474,'event_content','Enjoy an evening of pleasure with Krug x Vinyl, as the famed Champagne House takes over one of LA’s finest restaurants, Kali.  Revel in a selection of Krug Champagnes as winemaker Jérôme Jacoillot presents his musical selections to pair with each Champagne.\r\n\r\nCo-Owner/Chef Kevin Meehan will deliver a menu of bites to complement the wines and ensure that all senses are truly delighted. Champagnes to be enjoyed include different editions of Krug Grande Cuvée from Magnum &amp; Jeroboam, Krug Vintage 2004 and Krug Rosé.'),(26421,1474,'_event_content','field_5a621095d626c'),(26422,1474,'event_package',''),(26423,1474,'_event_package','field_5a6222a9f43c7'),(26424,1474,'event_passes_0_title','Krug x Vinyl Pass'),(26425,1474,'_event_passes_0_title','field_5a625f711c1ff'),(26426,1474,'event_passes_0_price','$130'),(26427,1474,'_event_passes_0_price','field_5a625fa91c200'),(26428,1474,'event_passes_0_description',''),(26429,1474,'_event_passes_0_description','field_5a625fc61c201'),(26430,1474,'event_passes','1'),(26431,1474,'_event_passes','field_5a625f5e1c1fe'),(26432,1474,'event_venue','136'),(26433,1474,'_event_venue','field_5a6224a7dde1d'),(26434,1474,'event_start_date','20180504'),(26435,1474,'_event_start_date','field_5a622aacf8cf9'),(26436,1474,'event_start_time','20:00:00'),(26437,1474,'_event_start_time','field_5a622acff8cfa'),(26438,1474,'event_end_time',''),(26439,1474,'_event_end_time','field_5a622b05f8cfb'),(26440,1474,'event_participant_groups','2'),(26441