(42824,2097,'_event_excerpt','field_5a621b80bbd03'),(42825,2097,'event_content','Join Jérôme Jacoillot, the Krug winemaker in charge of the iconic Clos du Mesnil as he takes you on a master class of Chardonnay through Krug Champagne.\r\n\r\nWines from the house including two vintages of the famed Krug Clos du Mesnil will be tasted, while Jérôme provides context on how he manages to respect the purity and singularity of this key varietal in Champagne. To illustrate the beauty of Chardonnay, Jérôme will be bringing from the cellars in Reims, Krug Clos du Mesnil Vintage 2004, which is the first time the wine will be presented in the United States.\r\n\r\n<strong>Wines to be poured:</strong>\r\n\r\nClos du Mesnil 2003\r\nVintage Brut 2003\r\nGrande Cuvée 159th Edition (Harvest 2003)\r\nClos du Mesnil 2004\r\nVintage Brut 2004\r\nGrande Cuvée 160th Edition (Harvest 2004)'),(42826,2097,'_event_content','field_5a621095d626c'),(42827,2097,'event_sales_status','0'),(42828,2097,'_event_sales_status','field_5a7e26c57772f'),(42829,2097,'event_package',''),(42830,2097,'_event_package','field_5a6222a9f43c7'),(42831,2097,'event_passes','1'),(42832,2097,'_event_passes','field_5a625f5e1c1fe'),(42833,2097,'event_venue','114'),(42834,2097,'_event_venue','field_5a6224a7dde1d'),(42835,2097,'event_start_date','20180504'),(42836,2097,'_event_start_date','field_5a622aacf8cf9'),(42837,2097,'event_start_time','16:00:00'),(42838,2097,'_event_start_time','field_5a622acff8cfa'),(42839,2097,'event_end_time','17:30:00'),(42840,2097,'_event_end_time','field_5a622b05f8cfb'),(42841,2097,'event_participant_groups_0_header','Speaker'),(42842,2097,'_event_participant_groups_0_header','field_5a6224e6d31dd'),(42843,2097,'event_participant_groups_0_producers',''),(42844,2097,'_event_participant_groups_0_producers','field_5a622caadb3a8'),(42845,2097,'event_participant_groups_0_chefs',''),(42846,2097,'_event_participant_groups_0_chefs','field_5a622c57db3a5'),(42847,2097,'event_participant_groups_0_sommelier