vent_participant_groups_1_speakers','field_5a622c92db3a7'),(42883,2099,'event_type','3'),(42884,2099,'_event_type','field_5a621223b7bc7'),(42885,2099,'event_excerpt','Enjoy a sumptuous tasting menu by Chef Walter Manzke celebrating Billecart-Salmon’s 200th Anniversary. Only those in attendance will have the opportunity to bid on the sole known Magnum of Nicolas Francois 1961. \r\n\r\nIf you prefer to purchase tickets by phone, please call one of the numbers below, leave your name and number and we will gladly reach out to take your order: <a href=\"tel://323.499.8678\">323.499.8678</a> and <a href=\"tel://323.937.9463\">323.937.9463</a>.'),(42886,2099,'_event_excerpt','field_5a621b80bbd03'),(42887,2099,'event_content','For our first annual Collector Champagne Luncheon, we are excited to celebrate the 200th anniversary of Billecart-Salmon with special guest Geoffrey Loisel, Director North America, Champagne Billecart-Salmon.\r\n\r\nAdding to the festivities, only guests at the luncheon will be able to bid on the sole known magnum of Nicolas Francois 1961. Sourced from the Domaine and presented by Geoffrey Loisel himself.\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-2042\" src=\"https://effervescencela.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/B--800x441.jpg\" alt=\"B-S farm house\" width=\"800\" height=\"441\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: #333333; cursor: text; font-family: Georgia,\'Times New Roman\',\'Bitstream Charter\',Times,serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px;\">C</span><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: #333333; cursor: text; font-family: Georgia,\'Times New Roman\',\'Bitstream Charter\',Times,serif; font