Thank you for being interested in pouring at Effervescence! Please fill out our <a href=\"https://effervescencela.com/contact/\">contact form</a> and we will get back to you with more information.'),(44765,2233,'_question_list_1_list_0_answer','field_5a6a164158e6a'),(44766,2233,'question_list_1_list','5'),(44767,2233,'_question_list_1_list','field_5a6a162458e68'),(44768,2233,'question_list_2_subhead','Media'),(44769,2233,'_question_list_2_subhead','field_5a6a160b58e67'),(44770,2233,'question_list_2_list_0_question','Are there press passes available for Effervescence?'),(44771,2233,'_question_list_2_list_0_question','field_5a6a163c58e69'),(44772,2233,'question_list_2_list_0_answer','Thank you for your interest in Effervescence! Please submit media inquiries and requests for information using our <a href=\"https://effervescencela.com/contact/\">contact form</a>.'),(44773,2233,'_question_list_2_list_0_answer','field_5a6a164158e6a'),(44774,2233,'question_list_2_list','2'),(44775,2233,'_question_list_2_list','field_5a6a162458e68'),(44776,2233,'post_content','If you have a FAQ that is not answered here, please reach out to us via our <a href=\"https://effervescencela.com/contact/\">contact page</a>.'),(44777,2233,'_post_content','field_5a7f067bcddaa'),(44778,2233,'post_banner','382'),(44779,2233,'_post_banner','field_5a7f0721daba2'),(44780,2233,'question_list_0_list_2_question','Where did Effervescence 2018 take place?'),(44781,2233,'_question_list_0_list_2_question','field_5a6a163c58e69'),(44782,2233,'question_list_0_list_2_answer','<ul>\r\n 	<li>The <a href=\"https://effervescencela.com/events/grand-champagne-tasting/\">Grand Champagne Tasting</a> and the <a href=\"https://effervescencela.com/events/bubbles-sparkling-wine-extravanga/\">More Bubbles Sparkling Wine Tasting</a> took place at the historic Avalon Hollywood.</li>\r\n 	<li>The master classes all took place at the Kimpton La Peer hotel in West Hollywood.</li>\r\n 	<li>The <a href=\"https://effervescencela.com/events/collectors-champagne-dinner/\">Krug Lovers Dinner</a> was held at Viale dei Romani in West Hollywood</li>\r\n 	<li>The <a href=\"https://effervescencela.com/events/collectors-champagne-lunch-republique-chef-walter-manzke/\">Billecart-Salmon Collector Champagne Dinner</a> and the <a href=\"https://effervescencela.com/events/champagne-gala-dinner/\">Gala Champagne Dinner</a> both took place at Republique restaurant.</li>\r\n 	<li>The <a href=\"https://effervescencela.com/events/evening-pleasure-krug-x-vinyl/\">An Evening of Pleasure: Krug x Viny</a><a href=\"https://effervescencela.com/events/evening-pleasure-krug-x-vinyl/\">l</a> event took place at KALI restaurant.</li>\r\n</ul>'),(44783,2233,'_question_list_0_list_2_answer','field_5a6a164158e6a'),(44784,2233,'question_list_0_list_3_question','Was there an age requirement to attend the events?'),(44785,2233,'_question_list_0_list_3_question','field_5a6a163c58e69'),(44786,2233,'question_list_0_list_3_answer','Yes, all our events are strictly 21 and above only.'),(44787,2233,'_question_list_0_list_3_answer','field_5a6a164158e6a'),(44788,2233,'question_list_2_list_1_question','Do you have a media kit available for Effervescence?'),(44789,2233,'_question_list_2_list_1_question','field_5a6a163c58e69'),(44790,2233,'question_list_2_list_1_answer','Please submit media inquiries and requests for information using our <a href=\"https://effervescencela.com/contact/\">contact form</a>.'),(44791,2233,'_question_list_2_list_1_answer','field_5a6a164158e6a'),(44792,2233,'question_list_0_list_4_question','Did the wines at the More Bubbles and Grand Champagne Tastings at the Avalon come with the price of the ticket?'),(44793,2233,'_question_list_0_list_4_question','field_5a6a163c58e69'),(44794,2233,'question_list_0_list_4_answer','Yes! The pass allowed for wine tastings from the attending producers at no additional cost.'),(44795,2233,'_question_list_0_list_4_answer','field_5a6a164158e6a'),(44796,2233,'question_list_1_list_1_qu