ner</a>\r\nJoin Krug winemaker Jérôme Jacoillot and a group of Krug lovers for a night of exclusive treasures and the cuisine of Chef Casey Lane.\r\n7:30pm\r\nViale dei Romani Restaurant\r\n\r\n[caption id=\"attachment_2156\" align=\"alignnone\" width=\"640\"]<img class=\"size-full wp-image-2156\" src=\"https://effervescencela.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/Krug-sign.jpg\" alt=\"Krug sign\" width=\"640\" height=\"480\" /> Krug reception at Viale dei Romani[/caption]\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h3>Friday, May 4, 2018</h3>\r\n<strong>Master Class</strong>\r\n<a href=\"/events/master-class-mature-champagnes/\">Mature Champagnes – How Champagne Ages Over the Years</a>\r\nSwedish Champagne expert Richard Juhlin, in a rare US appearance, will conduct a master class on how mature Champagne evolves through five decades.\r\n10:30am\r\nKimpton La Peer Hotel\r\n\r\n[caption id=\"attachment_2179\" align=\"alignnone\" width=\"598\"]<img class=\"size-full wp-image-2179\" src=\"https://effervescencela.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/Juhlin-cropped.jpg\" alt=\"Richard Juhlin\" width=\"598\" height=\"475\" /> Richard Juhlin on mature Champagnes[/caption]\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<a href=\"/events/collectors-champagne-lunch-republique/\">Billecart-Salmon Collector Champagne Luncheon</a>\r\nSumptuous tasting menu by Chef Walter Manzke celebrating Billecart-Salmon’s 200th Anniversary. Only those in attendance had the opportunity to bid on the sole known Magnum of Nicolas Francois 1961. Sourced from the Domaine and presented by Geoffrey Loisel, Director North America, Champagne Billecart-Salmon.\r\n12:30pm\r\nRépublique Restaurant\r\n\r\n[caption id=\"attachment_2151\" align=\"alignnone\" width=\"800\"]<img class=\"wp-image-2151 size-medium\" src=\"https://effervescencela.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/Trio20Collection20©Leif20Carlson_preview.jpeg-800x534.jpg\" alt=\"Billecart Salmon luncheon\" width=\"800\" height=\"534\" /> Billecart Salmon luncheon[/caption]\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong>Master Class</strong>\r\n<a href=\"/events/an-exploration-of-chardonnay-in-krug-champagne/\">An Exploration of Chardonnay in Krug</a>\r\nWinemaker of Krug Clos du Mesnil, Jérôme Jacoillot, takes us on an exploration of Chardonnay. This class also saw the American debut of Krug Clos du Mesnil 2004!\r\n4:00pm – 5:30pm\r\nKimpton La Peer Hotel\r\n\r\n[caption id=\"attachment_2162\" align=\"alignnone\" width=\"533\"]<img class=\"size-full wp-image-2162\" src=\"https://effervescencela.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/Jerome-cropped.jpg\" alt=\"Jerome on the meaning of Chardonnay\" width=\"533\" height=\"582\" /> Jérôme Jacoillot on the meaning of Chardonnay[/caption]\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<a href=\"/events/bubbles-sparkling-wine-extravanga/\">More Bubbles — Sparkling Wine Tasting</a>\r\nA walk-around style tasting featuring sparkling wines from Spain, USA, France, England, Italy, New Zealand and beyond.\r\n5:00pm – 9:00pm\r\nAvalon Hollywood\r\n\r\n[caption id=\"attachment_2125\" align=\"alignnone\" width=\"800\"]<img class=\"wp-image-2125 size-medium\" src=\"https://effervescencela.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/more-bubbles-avalon-effervescence-zane-roessell-5-04-2018-2878-7721_preview.jpeg-800x534.jpg\" alt=\"More Bubbles\" width=\"800\" height=\"534\" /> Glasses set up for the More Bubbles tasting at Avalon Hollywood[/caption]\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<a href=\"/events/evening-pleasure-krug-x-vinyl/\">An Evening of Pleasure: Krug x Vinyl</a>\r\nThe famed Champagne House and winemaker Jérôme Jacoillot took over one of LA’s finest restaurants, Kali, for a night of Krug, vinyl vibes &amp; dancing. It was a night of discovering the inner music of Krug.\r\n8:00pm\r\nKali Restaurant\r\n\r\n[caption id=\"attachment_2141\" align=\"alignnone\" width=\"800\"]<img class=\"wp-image-2141 size-medium\" src=\"https://effervescencela.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/krug-and-vinyl-kali-effervescence-zane-roessell-5-04-2018-2878-8660_preview.jpeg-800x534.jpg\" alt=\"Krug x Kali \" width=\"800\" height=\"534\" /> Krug and vinyl[/caption]\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h3>Saturday, May 5, 2018</h3>\r\n<b>Master Class\r\n</b> <a href=\"https://effervescencela.com/events/masterclass-champagne-hiking-richard-juhlin/\">Champagne Hiking – The Missing Piece</a>\r\n\r\n<strong><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: #333333; cursor: text; font-family: Georgia,\'Times New Roman\',\'Bitstream Charter\',Times,serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px;\">Richard Juhlin, author of The Scent of Champagne, on how our environment influences our perception of Champagne.</span>\r\n<span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: #333333; cursor: text; font-family: Georgia,\'Times New Roman\',\'Bitstream Charter\',Times,serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px;\"> 3:30pm</span>\r\n<span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: #333333; cursor: text; font-family: Georgia,\'Times New Roman\',\'Bitstream Charter\',Times,serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px;\"> Kimpton La Peer Hotel</span></strong>\r\n\r\n[caption id=\"attachment_2159\" align=\"alignnone\" width=\"756\"]<img class=\"size-medium wp-image-2159\" src=\"https://effervescencela.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/Juhlin-hiking-cropped-756x800.jpg\" alt=\"Richard Juhlin \" width=\"756\" height=\"800\" /> Richard Juhlin on \"Champagne Hiking\"[/caption]\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<a href=\"/events/grand-champagne-tasting/\">Grand Champagne Tasting</a>\r\nThe can’t miss event of Effervescence! A grand tasting tour of Champagne and all the region has to offer.\r\n1:00pm – 5:00pm\r\nAvalon Hollywood\r\n\r\n[caption id=\"attachment_2135\" align=\"alignnone\" width=\"800\"]<img class=\"wp-image-2135 size-medium\" src=\"https://effervescencela.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/grand-champagne-tasting-avalon-effervescence-zane-roessell-5-05-2018-2878-9468_preview.jpeg-800x534.jpg\" alt=\"Grand Champagne Tasting\" width=\"800\" height=\"534\" /> Attendees at the Grand Champagne Tasting at Avalon Hollywood[/caption]\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<a href=\"/events/champagne-gala-dinner/\">Champagne Gala Dinner</a>\r\nChef Walter Manzke hosted a Paulée-style banquet where enthusiasts and producers alike popped and shared their most treasured bottles of Champagne.\r\n7:00pm\r\nRépublique Restaurant\r\n\r\n[caption id=\"attachment_2138\" align=\"alignnone\" width=\"800\"]<img class=\"wp-image-2138 size-medium\" src=\"https://effervescencela.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/gala-dinner-republique-effervescence-zane-roessell-5-05-2018-2878-9754_preview.jpeg-800x534.jpg\" alt=\"Gala Dinner\" width=\"800\" height=\"534\" /> Table set up for the Champagne Gala Dinner[/caption]\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nFor more images from the different events, take a look at our <a href=\"https://effervescencela.com/effervescence-2018/\">2018 event page</a>!','Auto Draft','For anyone in love with bubbles, there was only one place to be on the first weekend of May - EFFERVESCENCE. During May 3-5, winemakers from around the world, their importers, an exceptional team of sommeliers and Los Angeles\' own star chefs Walter Manzke, Casey Lane & Kevin Meehan all teamed up for America\'s ode to all things sparkling. Thank you to everyone that helped make EFFERVESCENCE 2018 such a success!\r\n\r\nSign up below for news on next year\'s event and scroll down to see an overview of the inaugural events.','auto-draft','closed','closed','','','','','2019-01-24 21:27:35','2019-01-24 21:27:35','',0,'https://effervescencela.com/?post_type=efrvs_event&#038;p=2271',0,'efrvs_event','',0),(2272,5,'2019-01-24 21:32:18','0000-00-00 00:00:00','','Auto Draft','','auto-draft','closed','closed','','','','','2019-01-24 21:32:18','0000-00-00 00:00:00','',0,'https://effervescencela.com/?post_type=efrvs_event&p=2272',0,'efrvs_event','',0);
