 or more above sea-level, steeply sloped, and consist of almost white limestone-rich clay with a lot of stones. He now has more than 10 acres of vineyards in Cigliè and is making vibrant and intriguing wines from grapes grown there and transported back to Serralunga, about 30 minutes away, to be vinified. (Higher altitude tends to bring cooler nights, which allows the fruit to retain more acidity, making it perfect for fresh whites and sparkling wines.)'),(1790,152,'_term_description','field_5a68eea623c97'),(1791,152,'term_outbound_url','http://ettoregermano.com/en'),(1792,152,'_term_outbound_url','field_5a68cda3135c9'),(1793,152,'term_logo','1708'),(1794,152,'_term_logo','field_5a68eda7a5824'),(1795,152,'term_photo',''),(1796,152,'_term_photo','field_5a68fba28eade'),(1797,152,'producers_clone_term_meta',''),(1798,152,'_producers_clone_term_meta','field_5a68fdaed90df'),(1799,153,'term_banner_image',''),(1800,153,'_term_banner_image','field_5a85c6b7cac4a'),(1801,153,'term_lname','Domaine'),(1802,153,'_term_lname','field_5a68f2ed46aa0'),(1803,153,'term_description',''),(1804,153,'_term_description','field_5a68eea623c97'),(1805,153,'term_outbound_url','https://vintage59.com/our-portfolio/pfister_alsace/'),(1806,153,'_term_outbound_url','field_5a68cda3135c9'),(1807,153,'term_logo','1893'),(1808,153,'_term_logo','field_5a68eda7a5824'),(1809,153,'term_photo',''),(1810,153,'_term_photo','field_5a68fba28eade'),(1811,153,'producers_clone_term_meta',''),(1812,153,'_producers_clone_term_meta','field_5a68fdaed90df'),(1813,154,'term_banner_image',''),(1814,154,'_term_banner_image','field_5a85c6b7cac4a'),(1815,154,'term_lname','Le'),(1816,154,'_term_lname','field_5a68f2ed46aa0'),(1817,154,'term_description',''),(1818,154,'_term_description','field_5a68eea623c97'),(1819,154,'term_outbound_url','https://vintage59.com/our-portfolio/rocher_des_violettes_montlouis/'),(1820,154,'_term_outbound_url','field_5a68cda3135c9'),(1821,154,'term_logo','1894'),(1822,154,'_term_logo','field_5a68e